items.name: top14-ML-predictor
items.description: Deep Learning model built with PyTorch to predict French Top 14 rugby match scores. Features specific metrics (offloads, defense, tackle), RobustScaler normalization, and Early Stopping to prevent overfitting. Includes a full season simulator to forecast the final league rankings with all the results of the coming games.
